<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ugly-adj">ugly <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʌɡli/    美 /'ʌɡli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>难看的；丑陋的:</strong></h4>
<p>反 beautiful </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an ugly building 
难看的建筑物</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>令人不快的；可怕的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an ugly smell 
令人作呕的气味</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>ugly incident</strong> 
可怕的事件</p></div></div>